name: Laporan Pemasukan Barang Per Dokumen
query:
select
`tabPemasukan Barang`.jenis_dokumen_bc as "Jenis Dokumen:Select:50",
`tabPemasukan Barang`.nomor_dokumen_bc as "No. Dokumen:Data:80",
`tabPemasukan Barang`.tanggal_dokumen as "Tanggal Dokumen:Date:80",
`tabPemasukan Barang`.purchase_receipt_no as "No. Surat Jalan:int:150",
`tabPemasukan Barang`.delivery_date as "Tgl. Surat Jalan:Date:80",
`tabPemasukan Barang`.pengirim_supplier as "Pengirim:Link/Supplier:80",
`tabBarang Masuk Item`.item_code as "Kode Barang:Link/Item:150",
`tabBarang Masuk Item`.item_name as "Nama Barang:Data:200",
`tabBarang Masuk Item`.uom as "Satuan:Link/UOM:80",
`tabBarang Masuk Item`.qty as "Jumlah:Float:80",
`tabBarang Masuk Item`.amount as "Nilai:Currency:150"



from
`tabPemasukan Barang`,`tabBarang Masuk Item`

where
`tabPemasukan Barang`.docstatus=1
